Description_lang: Reduces the cooldown of Ring of Peace by ${$s1/-1000} sec and Song of Chi-Ji's cast time is reduced by ${$s2/-1000}.1 sec.

description_blz.en_US: Reduces the cooldown of Ring of Peace by 5 sec and Song of Chi-Ji's cast time is reduced by 0.5 sec.

description_blz.ko_KR: 평화의 고리의 재사용 대기시간이 5초만큼, 츠지의 노래의 시전 시간이 0.5초만큼 감소합니다.
